{"type": "article", "id": 19334, "title": "蜂蜜包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 116, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104213YeZjNFscx1iS2Eh5.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t俄罗斯的设计师 Maksim Arbuzov 认为，蜂蜜应该保持它本来的样子，于是用透明的六角形瓶子做蜂蜜的瓶身，让蜂蜜自然的颜色透出来。木质的盖子也是六角形的，盖子里直接连接了蜂蜜棒，很方便。为了让这些蜂蜜在货架上排列成蜂窝的样子，设计师在瓶子下面空出了放盖子的凹槽，能稳固地排成一面。<a href=\"http://www.maksimarbuzov.com/#/honey/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145849SjQ9uynN4lVg2mwe.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66712329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145850RYgLDhCUVlJjM0GK.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66712329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261458508Gb3e0XgpORsqKcE.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"487\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66712329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145851eskQ7AR913bEGPHh.jpg\" width=\"730\" height=\"511\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}